                    "```",
                    "",
                    "---",
                    "",
                    " Manage the trust database.",
                    "",
                    " The trust database is located at |$XDG_STATE_HOME|/nvim/trust.",
                    "",
                    "@*return* `success` — true if operation was successful",
                    "",
